Q. Assume you are given the table below on Uber transactions made by users. Write a query to obtain the third transaction of every user. 
Output the user id, spend and transaction date.

A. WITH COUNTED_TRANSACTIONS AS
(SELECT USER_ID, SPEND, TRANSACTION_DATE,
ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY USER_ID ORDER BY TRANSACTION_DATE) AS RN
FROM transactions)

SELECT USER_ID, SPEND, TRANSACTION_DATE FROM COUNTED_TRANSACTIONS
WHERE RN = 3;

